                "invariants for sliding windows",
                "trade memory for time deliberately",
                "state complexity before optimizing"
              ],
              "domains": ["arrays"]
            },
            {
              "id": "trees",
              "label": "Trees & graphs",
              "fundamentals": [
                "pick traversal for the question",
                "handle null and empty base cases",
                "recursive vs iterative trade-offs"
